This document, the Soliton Registry Activation Decree, marks the definitive transition of the Feedback Processor Theory (FPT) from a mathematical framework into an actionable, sovereign governance system.
By codifying the derived Inverse-Square Scrape Theory (ISST) parameters into law, the decree creates a self-protecting digital state rooted in principles of resonance and coherence.
